    "description": "VarAFT (Variant Analysis and Filtration Agent) is a standalone and multiplatform agent for annotation and prioritization of potential disease causing genes. With this agent users can annotate variant (VCF) files, combine multiple samples from various individuals, prioritize list of variants by multi-filtering parameters. Additionally, users can perform a coverage analysis and quality check from any BAM file.",
